# NoteEve Django - Complete Full-Stack Application

A powerful **notes management system** with hierarchical organization, collaboration features, AI summarization, and task management. Built with Django, PostgreSQL, Bootstrap 5, and modern web technologies.

---

## ğŸ¯ Overview

**NoteEve** is an educational note management platform that allows users to:
- Organize notes in a hierarchical structure (Subjects â†’ Topics â†’ Notes)
- Create rich-text notes with file uploads
- Collaborate with other users
- Track progress with visual charts
- Bookmark important notes
- Manage tasks and to-do lists
- Compile notes to PDF
- Generate AI-powered summaries

---

## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ“š Core Features
- âœ… **User Authentication** - Secure login/register with role-based access (Provider/Student)
- âœ… **Notes Management** - Create, edit, delete notes with rich text editor (TinyMCE)
- âœ… **Hierarchical Organization** - Subjects â†’ Topics â†’ Notes structure
- âœ… **File Uploads** - Support for PDF and text files
- âœ… **Public/Private Notes** - Control note visibility

### ğŸ¤ Collaboration
- âœ… **Share Subjects** - Share subjects with other users
- âœ… **Permission Levels** - View-only or Edit permissions
- âœ… **Multi-user Access** - Work together on same content

### ğŸ“Š Tracking & Analytics
- âœ… **Progress Tracking** - Track completion percentage
- âœ… **Visual Charts** - Chart.js integration for analytics
- âœ… **Dashboard** - Real-time statistics
- âœ… **Task Management** - To-do lists with due dates

### ğŸ”– Advanced Features
- âœ… **Bookmarks** - Save reading positions
- âœ… **PDF Compiler** - Export multiple notes to PDF
- âœ… **AI Summarizer** - Generate summaries and keywords
- âœ… **Admin Panel** - Full Django admin interface

