## ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Models (9 Total)

| Model | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| **CustomUser** | Extended user with roles (Provider/Student) |
| **Subject** | Top-level organization unit |
| **Topic** | Second-level under subject |
| **Note** | Actual note content |
| **Bookmark** | User bookmarks for notes |
| **Task** | To-do list items |
| **Progress** | Completion tracking |
| **Collaboration** | Multi-user sharing |
| **Summary** | AI-generated summaries |

